'''波江座51b'''（'''51 Eridani b'''）是位於[[波江座|波江座]]的一顆環繞恆星[[波江座51|波江座51]]的[[太陽系外行星|太陽系外行星]]<ref>{{Cite web |last=Choi |first=Charles |date=August 13, 2015 |title=Found! 'Young Jupiter,' the Smallest Exoplanet Directly Seen by Telescope |url=http://www.space.com/30248-young-jupiter-smallest-directly-imaged-exoplanet.html |accessdate=August 15, 2015 |archive-date=2019-05-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190520055508/https://www.space.com/30248-young-jupiter-smallest-directly-imaged-exoplanet.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 概要 ==
波江座51b於2015年8月宣布發現，但在2014年12月由{{link-en|卡夫利粒子天文物理與宇宙學研究所|Kavli Institute for Particle Astrophysics and Cosmology}}領導的國際研究團隊已在{{link-en|雙子星行星成像儀|Gemini Planet Imager}}拍攝的影像中發現到它。波江座51b距離地球約100光年，年齡約2000萬年<ref>{{cite web |last=Hadhazy |first=Adam |date=August 13, 2015 |title='Young Jupiter' 51 Eridani b: Why Directly Imaging an Exoplanet Is Big |work=space.com |url=http://www.space.com/30238-young-jupiter-exoplanet-51-eridani-b-explained.html |accessdate=August 15, 2015 |archive-date=2019-04-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428135253/https://www.space.com/30238-young-jupiter-exoplanet-51-eridani-b-explained.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

天文學家推測波江座51b的質量大約是木星的2倍，並且是至今發現的系外行星中[[甲烷|甲烷]]譜線最強烈者<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/51-eridani-b-astronomers-discover-young-planet-that-looks-like-jupiter-100-light-years-away-10454531.html|date|title = Astronomers Discover Young Planet That Looks Like Jupiter 100 Light Years Away|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2021-05-28|archive-url = https://archive.today/20210528001021/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/science/51-eridani-b-astronomers-discover-young-planet-that-looks-like-jupiter-100-light-years-away-10454531.html%7Cdate|dead-url = no}}</ref>。它的表面溫度是650°C，遠高於太陽系中體積與它最相近的木星表面的−145°C<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.space.com/30239-young-jupiter-exoplanet-51-eridani-b.html|title = Exoplanet 51 Eridani b: A Red-Hot Young Jupiter Around Distant Star (Infographic)|date = |accessdate = |website = |publisher = |last = |first = |archive-date = 2018-07-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180724153916/https://www.space.com/30239-young-jupiter-exoplanet-51-eridani-b.html|dead-url = no}}</ref>。天文學家使用雙子星行星成像儀的光譜儀對波江座51b進行觀測，於2015年8月宣布在該行星大氣層中發現水的存在<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-33922503 |title = Young 'alien Jupiter' planet discovered |date = 14 August 2015 |accessdate = 22 August 2015 |website = BBC |publisher =  |last =  |first =  |archive-date = 2018-11-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181105232650/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/science-environment-33922503 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。在發現波江座51b以前，以直接攝影法發現的系外行星質量都遠高於木星<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.scientificamerican.com/article/astronomers-glimpse-a-young-jupiter-51-eridani-b/ |title = Astronomers Glimpse a Young Jupiter, 51 Eridani b |date = 14 August 2015 |accessdate = 22 August 2015 |website = Scientific American |publisher =  |last = Billings |first = Lee |archive-date = 2018-11-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181106225713/https://www.scientificamerican.com/article/astronomers-glimpse-a-young-jupiter-51-eridani-b/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

